Package: choicedata
Type: Package
Title: Simulate, Read, and Visualize Choice Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lennart", "Oelschl\u00e4ger", 
           email = "oelschlaeger.lennart@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5421-9313"))
Description: Provides a set of objects and methods designed to facilitate the 
    simulation, reading and visualization of choice data generated by various 
    types of probit and logit models (including binary, multinomial, ordered, 
    ranked, mixed, and latent class models) and to compute the likelihood of 
    these models for given data.
